page.title: 20ACKNOWLEDGEMENTS. L'MOUTH.
page.content: We,Steven Andrews,Janet Cordiner, Lyndsey Hewson,Fiona Mackenzie, Marie Osborn,Lynne Robertson, Kirsteen Sangster,Ainsley Smith, Karen Souter,James Sumner, Primary 7 pupils of St.Gerardine Primary School,Lossiemouth, wish to give thanks to the following people for the help and information which they supplied to us, Moray District Planning Department, Scottish Agriculture Department, Mr. J. Scott, Harbour-Master, Squ.Ldr.A.Sumner,R.A.F.Lossiemouth, Mrs.N.Forbes,Fish-Processing Plant, Mr.A.Thomson,Golf Professional Mrs.M.Morris,our teacher and last but not least Mrs.C.T.Edwards,our Head Teacher. 4th July 1985.
